10T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"唔係間間公司都需要cross-platform"},{"pid":"cc2420d3d676419009fa62cae6bb7b0824f619da","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559633037ccd39d043c7887e4868c45f44e68f75","tid":2482744,"uid":248650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"想問問<br />\n<br />\n如果rn可以寫個app比iOS Android用<br />\n<br />\n咁仲有冇公司會用swift 寫iOS<br />\n然後Android 用Java 咁分開寫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為想知既然有rn呢類cross platform 既<br />\n咁點解要學swift?<br />\n有冇咩rn做踎到一定要用swift?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"點解有普通話，重仍然要有廣東話上海話？<br />\n<br />\nRN 呢個平台唔係apple 同 google 出，就注定佢唔會追貼底層平台既發展。咁當然唔係個個app 都要最新既OS 功能，呢個就係RN 既市場空間。<br />\n<br />\n而RN 真係好high level, 變左RN 既 developer 唔落番去native底層無法做啲嘢去做系統level 工作。做一個industrial strength 既app 結果係要識2 個platform 變成要識 3 個 platform."},{"pid":"266c38ba41e01f124f6e2d9d0cc10907c39aa4a7","tid":2482744,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559633037ccd39d043c7887e4868c45f44e68f75","tid":2482744,"uid":248650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"想問問<br />\n<br />\n如果rn可以寫個app比iOS Android用<br />\n<br />\n咁仲有冇公司會用swift 寫iOS<br />\n然後Android 用Java 咁分開寫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為想知既然有rn呢類cross platform 既<br />\n咁點解要學swift?<br />\n有冇咩rn做踎到一定要用swift?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"都遇過幾個原因 <br />\n有次做integration要用到sdk咪要用native"},{"pid":"e0d40ee935356cba80eae68efd2f02737716424c","tid":2482744,"uid":248650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T16:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁唔知而家做app<br />\n如果一定要iOS Android兩邊都要有<br />\n<br />\n係咪一定用rn 果類<br />\n而唔會考慮用native language 呢"},{"pid":"c25b507ec57356ee3cf2230e32bd997c6ef6b62b","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0d40ee935356cba80eae68efd2f02737716424c","tid":2482744,"uid":248650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T16:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁唔知而家做a