00Z","msg":"KMM<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/lp/mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkotlinlang.org%2Flp%2Fmobile%2F&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=a7eb4ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kotlinlang.org/lp/mobile/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"覺得幾正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"想睇下從iOS dev 角度點睇呢壇嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"寫 cross platform library for business logic <br />\n如果自己 projrct / 公司許可，加上本身識 kotlin 咁都無話唔得嘅<br />\n<br />\n我自己首選會用 C++，如果唔熟，要由零開始學隻新，咁我覺得 go gomobile 好過 kotlin，用途廣啲。除非諗住順便學埋寫 Android app<br />\n<br />\n唔怕 performance 問題可以用 js 來 call native function (eg iOS JSCore)，仲可以 hot patch<br />\n或者有啲寫開 unity 嘅可能會揀用 Lua"},{"pid":"5d4b44d8658110e4f0beb7f255aa0e5b3eb5986f","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067cf1d50af37ee0da873754c0f90d210cc95e9c","tid":2482744,"uid":3,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"126998651d4efc4bd387991ca9b3bfcf8e91fe5e","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2df108a8c97956e5fb3ad17d1c73542547c82bb","tid":2482744,"uid":70400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"覺得幾正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"想睇下從iOS dev 角度點睇呢壇嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"寫 cross platform library for business logic <br />\n如果自己 projrct / 公司許可，加上本身識 kotlin 咁都無話唔得嘅<br />\n<br />\n我自己首選會用 C++，如果唔熟，要由零開始學隻新，咁我覺得 go gomobile 好過 kotlin，用途廣啲。除非諗住順便學埋寫 Android app<br />\n<br />\n唔怕 performance 問題可以用 js 來 call native function (eg iOS JSCore)，仲可以 hot patch<br />\n或者有啲寫開 unity 嘅可能會揀用 Lua"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"c++ 又要寫一堆JNI code, 結果又要map 一層變番做java/kotlin, 用黎做serialization. <br />\n以前試過用go 寫native library 放落android, 不過有哂用C++ 寫既所有問題，外加Go 個runtime library 勁大，不過呢點唔知而家有無改變 。<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意shared code 係 java 定 swift, 不過我希望係code generation 而唔係native share library. 即例如swift 通過某種gradle plugin 變成kotlin code, 又或直接generate byte code 都OK."},{"pid":"0463d4b870a6dca9693e4ed599f77263fe829970","tid":2482744,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"用React<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐fb"},{"pid":"906963e63690364e10b95e3ebb453731e5a7a47d","tid":2482744,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067cf1d50af37ee0da873754c0f90d210cc95e9c","tid":2482744,"uid":3,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"126998651d4efc4bd387991ca9b3bfcf8e91fe5e","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2df108a8c97956e5fb3ad17d1c73542547c82bb","tid":2482744,"uid":70400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"覺得幾正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"想睇下從iOS dev 角度點睇呢壇嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"寫 cross platform library for business logic <br />\n如果自己 projrct / 公司許可，加上本身識 kotlin 咁都無話唔得嘅<br />\n<br />\n我自己首選會用 C++，如果唔熟，要由零開始學隻新，咁我覺得 go gomobile 好過 kotlin，用途廣啲。除非諗住順便學埋寫 Android app<br />\n<br />\n唔怕 performance 問題可以用 js 來 call native function (eg iOS JSCore)，仲可以 hot patch<br />\n或者有啲寫開 unity 嘅可能會揀用 Lua"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c286c0a1c9c214e4bb754d440cb87daa786b2508","tid":2482744,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126998651d4efc4bd387991ca9b3bfcf8e91fe5e","tid":2482744,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2df108a8c97956e5fb3ad17d1c73542547c82bb","tid":2482744,"uid":70400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da968329cf253ae8822ed78e